agent_selection_prompt:
Analyze this decision for risk assessment and recommend 4 specialist risk evaluation agents.

Subject: {subject}

Context: {context}

Each agent must score these dimensions: technical_risk, business_risk, operational_risk, mitigation_quality.
Note: For risk dimensions, higher scores mean LOWER risk (10 = minimal risk, 0 = critical risk).

Respond ONLY with a JSON array of agent definitions:
[
  {
    "agent_name": "Specific Name",
    "role": "Area of Expertise",
    "focus": "What this agent evaluates",
    "evaluation_criteria": ["criterion 1", "criterion 2", "criterion 3"]
  }
]
